        "authors": "Charles H. Cox, Edward I. Ackerman, Gary E. Betts et al.",
        "year": 2006,
        "venue": "IEEE transactions on microwave theory and techniques",
        "citation_count": 500,
        "abstract": "The authors correct an error in their original article (see ibid., vol.54, no.2, p.906-20, Feb. 2006).",
