        "citation_count": 25,
        "abstract": "Abstract A field‐trial system is presented in this paper to demonstrate that radio‐over‐fiber (RoF) techniques can be successfully applied to the remoting of a large antenna array for radio astronomical applications. © 2005 Wiley Periodicals, Inc. Microwave Opt Technol Lett 46: 48–54, 2005; Published online in Wiley InterScience (www.interscience.wiley.com). DOI 10.1002/mop.20898",
