    {
        "doi": "10.1063/1.4788696",
        "s2_id": "a3fb4a9901949a7b3ac79960e82421aaf8c1a932",
        "title": "Interferometric measurement of the pyroelectric coefficient in lithium niobate",
        "authors": "S. T. Popescu, A. Petris, V. Vlad",
        "year": 2013,
        "venue": "",
        "citation_count": 25,
        "abstract": "We report the measurement of pyroelectric field in LiNbO3 by introducing a new method, based on optical interferometry. The pyroelectric coefficient of the congruent LiNbO3 crystals has been determined by this method and the value obtained for it, ∼95 μC/(m2 · K), is consistent with previous results reported in literature, obtained by other methods.",
