    {
        "doi": "10.1364/josab.27.001707",
        "s2_id": "56fcca2ec2b0fcf1f481d26afcb94c4c1a926196",
        "title": "Harmonic and supercontinuum generation in quadratic and cubic nonlinear optical media",
        "authors": "S. Wabnitz, V. Kozlov",
        "year": 2010,
        "venue": "",
        "citation_count": 25,
        "abstract": "We present numerical simulations by means of the generalized nonlinear envelope equation of harmonic and supercontinuum generation induced by femtosecond pump pulses in optical media with both quadratic and third-order nonlinearities. Application examples to higher harmonic generation in periodically poled lithium niobate and optical parametric generation of a mid-infrared continuum in gallium arsenide are discussed.",
