        "abstract": "We demonstrate a thin-film LiNbO3 Mach-Zehnder modulator with polymer edge coupler. The modulator exhibits a half-wave voltage of 2 V, insertion loss less than 5 dB and modulation speed up to 128 Gb s−1.",
