        "authors": "U. Krishnamachari, S. Ristic, A. Ramaswamy et al.",
        "year": 2011,
        "venue": "",
        "citation_count": 2,
        "abstract": "Abstract An ultracompact coherent receiver with negative feedback was developed for highly linear phase demodulation.The receiver demonstrates a spur‐free dynamic range of 122 dB Hz 2/3 at a signal frequency of 300 MHz. © 2011 Wiley Periodicals, Inc. Microwave Opt Technol Lett 53:2343–2345, 2011; View this article online at wileyonlinelibrary.com. DOI 10.1002/mop.26236",
        "pdf_url": "",
